title: Macross F Music Clip Shuu: Nyankuri

synonyms: Macross Frontier Music Clip Shuu: Nyankuri
Macross Frontier Music Clip Collection: Nyankuri
alternative_titles.ja: マクロスF MUSIC CLIP集 娘クリ

synopsis:
Sheryl Nome, the acclaimed Galactic Fairy, views herself first and foremost as a singer—existing solely to be an instrument of her melody and rhythm. Ranka Lee, on the other hand, finds herself inadvertently reborn as the Super-Dimension Cinderella through her energetic singing. Driven by their shared passion for song and drawn together by their love for a pilot, the two songstresses from Macross F meet once again in Macross F Music Clip Shuu: Nyankuri to deliver an original animated collection of music videos and character clips.

[Written by MAL Rewrite]
